---
const { email } = Astro.props;
---

<section
  id="contacto"
  class="scroll-mt-[100px] bg-gradient-to-tr from-slate-300 to-blue-50 py-10 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-20 space-y-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-start flex-1 mb-10 md:mb-0 md:mr-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Contáctanos</h2>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6 text-justify w-full md:w-2/3">
      Si tienes alguna pregunta o necesitas más información, no dudes en
      contactarnos. Estamos aquí para ayudarte y brindarte la atención que
      mereces.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4 mb-6 text-slate-600 w-full">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
        <img src="/mail.svg" alt="email" class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7" />
        <p class="break-all">{email}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
        <img src="/phone.svg" alt="phoneNumber" class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7" />
        <p>+123-456-7890</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
        <img src="/clock.svg" alt="clock" class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7" />
        <p>Lunes a viernes: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
        <img src="/clock.svg" alt="clock" class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7" />
        <p>Sábados y domingos: 11:00 AM - 4:00 PM</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
    <form class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
      <input
        type="text"
        placeholder="Nombre"
        class="w-full p-3 border border-slate-400 rounded-lg"
      />
      <input
        type="email"
        placeholder="Correo electrónico"
        class="w-full p-3 border border-slate-400 rounded-lg"
      />
      <textarea
        placeholder="Mensaje"
        class="w-full p-3 border border-slate-400 rounded-lg h-32"></textarea>
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
      >
        Enviar
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
